sum of two numbers-L1

Define a function which can compute the sum of two numbers using recursion.

sample input:

4

8

Sample output:

12

import java.util.*;
class sotn
{
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        int a=sc.nextInt();
        int b=sc.nextInt();
        main s=new main();
        int c=s.add(a,b);
        System.out.println(c);
    }
}
class main
{
    int add(int a,int b)
    {
        return a+b;
    }
}
    
